There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsrose##1
 3. the french is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the mexican is the person watching action movies##1
10. the american is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the turkish##1
12. the person who growsazalea is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
