 2. the security-guard is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the person eating corn##1
 6. the person eating potato is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 9. the person eating pear is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the analyst is the person eating tomato##1
12. the analyst is the person eating tomato##1
13. the person eating pepper is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
