 2. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the person eating radish is between the person eating cherry and the person eating grapes##2
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person eating cherry is the person driving the train##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
15. the person eating radish is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
