.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, satire, animation, drama, thriller, documentary, musical
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, metal, punk, reggae, salsa, trance
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
 7. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
15. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Movie-Genre           | satire | documentary | thriller | animation  | musical   | drama | spy      |
| Music-Genre   | trance | metal        | salsa    | reggae     | punk     | house   | d&b        |
| Pet           | bird   | ferret       | mouse    | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake   | chinchilla |

