.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, cooking, dancing, gardening, hiking, photography, woodworking
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, coffee, mirinda, juice, hot-chocolate, cola
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, scooter, ship, snowmobile, taxi, trike
 1. the person driving the trike is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 2. the person driving the trike is the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking juice##1
13. the person driving the ship is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | dancing  | photography | gardening  | woodworking | cooking | hiking | baking |
| Beverage         | mirinda | coffee    | fanta        | juice      | hot-chocolate     | 7up   | cola |
| Transport   | scooter  | quad-bike   | snowmobile | taxi        | ship    | trike  | boat   |

