.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, bartender, dancer, firefighter, mechanic, photographer, videographer
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, ferret, frog, horse, fish, rabbit
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, handball, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the videographer##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the photographer is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the owner of the cat is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is between the dancer and the person who's sport is soccer##2
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
14. the owner of the cat is the person who's sport is soccer##1
15. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Job           | dancer      | accountant | mechanic | bartender   | photographer | firefighter | videographer |
| Pet   | rabbit | ferret   | cat   | frog | chinchilla        | horse       | fish       |
| Sport         | handball    | golf       | soccer   | skiing      | volleyball   | ice-hockey  | snowboarding |

